SELECT * FROM CVM_TYPE_OF_OPERATION WHERE TRADE_GOOD_TYPE_ID = [[trade_good_type_id]] AND SUPPLY_CHAIN_ACTOR_TYPE_ID = [[supply_chain_actor_type_id]]
select VERIFICATION_ID from CVM_VERIFICATION where RVS_ID=[[id_rvs]] and RVS_VERIFIED_ID = [[id_rvs_verified]]
select * from CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT where CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT.VERIFICATION_ID = [[id_verification]]

select * from CVM_DELEGATION inner join CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT on CVM_DELEGATION.VERIFICATION_RESULT_ID= CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT.VERIFICATION_RESULT_ID where CVM_DELEGATION.DELEGATOR_ID=[[id_supplier]] and CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT.VERIFICATION_ID = [[id_verification]]
select * from CVM_DELEGATION where CVM_DELEGATION.DELEGATOR_ID=[[id_supplier]]
SELECT * FROM CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT WHERE VERIFICATION_RESULT

select * from CVM_DELEGATION inner join CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT on CVM_DELEGATION.VERIFICATION_RESULT_ID= CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT.VERIFICATION_RESULT_ID inner join CVM_VERIFICATION on CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT.VERIFICATION_ID= CVM_VERIFICATION.VERIFICATION_ID where CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT.VERIFICATION_RESULT_ID=[[id_verification_result]] and CVM_DELEGATION.DELEGATOR_ID = [[id_supplier]]
SELECT * FROM CVM_VERIFICATION WHERE ARTICLE_ID =[[id_article]]

SELECT SYSDATE from DUAL

UPDATE CVM_SUPPLY_CHAIN_STRUCTURE SET SUPPLY_OBJECT_CHILD_ID =[[supply_object_child_id]],SUPPLY_OBJECT_CHILD_NAME = [[supply_object_child_name]],MODIFIED_TIMESTAMP=[[modified_timestamp]] WHERE PARENT_SUPPLY_CHAIN_ID = [[parent_supply_chain_id]] AND SUPPLY_CHAIN_ID = [[supply_chain_id]] AND SUPPLY_OBJECT_ID =[[supply_object_id]] AND RELATIONSHIP_TYPE = [[relationship_type]]
UPDATE CVM_DELEGATION SET DELEGATED_ID=[[id_subsupplier]] WHERE DELEGATOR_ID=[[id_supplier]] and DELEGATED_ID is null and VERIFICATION_RESULT_ID = [[id_verification_result]]
UPDATE CVM_SUPPLIER_DOCUMENT_DETAILS SET VALID_FROM = [[valid_from]], VALID_TILL = [[valid_till]], MODIFIED_TIMESTAMP = [[modified_timestamp]] WHERE DOC_NUMBER =[[doc_number]]
UPDATE CVM_REQUIREMENT_OBJECT_TRACKER SET CONNECTION_COUNTER = [[connection_counter]] WHERE SUPPLY_OBJECT_ID = [[supply_object_id]] AND REQUIREMENT_ID = [[requirement_id]]

UPDATE CVM_SUBSUPPLIER_DETAILS SET GLNCODE=[[gln_code]], LEGALNAME=[[legal_name]], LEGALCODE=[[legal_code]], LEGAL_ADDRESS=[[legal_address]], GPSCOORDINATES=[[gls_coordinates]], SUBSUPPLIER_TYPE=[[type]], MATERIAL_CATEGORY=[[material_category]], SUBTYPE=[[sub_type]], PROCESS=[[process]], MODIFIED_TIMESTAMP=[[modified_date]], COUNTRY = [[country]] WHERE SUB_SUPPLIER_ID = [[id_supplier]]

UPDATE CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT SET NUMBER_RESULT = [[numberResult]], INTEGER_RESULT = [[integerResult]], TEXT_RESULT = [[textResult]], RESULT_COMMENT = [[comment]], MODIFIED_TIMESTAMP = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, IS_VERIFIED = [[is_verified]], HAS_FEEDBACK = [[has_feedback]] WHERE VERIFICATION_RESULT_ID = [[id_verification_result]]

UPDATE CVM_VERIFICATION_RESULT SET NUMBER_RESULT = [[numberResult]], INTEGER_RESULT = [[integerResult]], TEXT_RESULT = [[textResult]], RESULT_COMMENT = [[comment]], MODIFIED_TIMESTAMP = now(), IS_VERIFIED = [[is_verified]], FILENAME=[[fileName]], HAS_FEEDBACK = true, FILE_CONTENT= lo_from_bytea(0,[[file_content]]::bytea)
WHERE VERIFICATION_RESULT_ID = [[id_verification_result]]
